  "instructions": [
    "In a large ceramic tagine, combine the papaya, tomatoes, chilies, peanuts, mint, fish sauce, sugar, salt, and black pepper, and toss to combine.",
    "In a separate bowl, mix together the coconut cream and lime juice, and set aside.",
    "Place the green beans over the papaya mixture in the tagine, and steam for 5 minutes over a bain-marie water bath.",
    "Remove the tagine from the heat, and stir in the coconut cream mixture and chopped cilantro.",
    "Serve the salad immediately, garnished with a lime wedge and a sprinkle of mint leaves.",
    "Adjust the seasoning with fish sauce, sugar, or lime juice to taste."
